(ii) by the insertion of the following paragraphs after paragraph (aj):“(ak) the National Treasury Management Agency in the performance of the functions conferred on it under theHome Building Finance Ireland Act 2018insofar as it relates to records concerning the following:(i) providers or potential providers of finance (including loans) to Home Building Finance Ireland or any HBFI group entity;
